        r.select_table_dropdown("100")
        assert isinstance(r.is_table_data_present(), str),"Table data not present"
        r.scroll_to_element(r.TOTAL_CALLS)
        r.do_click(r.EXPORT_BUTTON)
        r.do_click(r.EXPORT_SUB_BUTTON)
